      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but i've heard that as long as you're drinking enough water it helps balance everything out. if i just start drinking way more water and focus on staying hydrated, will that fix the nausea and shaking? i'm really trying to avoid a doctor's visit if i can just manage it at home.",
